content=["<dl>",
"<dt><a href='#Section0'>Migraine attack</a></dt>",
"<dd id='Section0'>",
"<p><strong>Sign & Symptoms:</strong> May be indistinguishable clinically.Presence of migraine may cause motion sickness to develop more rapidly in the appropriate setting.Migraine may be accompanied by aura and usually persists for hours beyond the motion exposure.",
"<br><strong>Test:</strong> There are no laboratory tests for differential diagnosis. Head imaging may exclude alternative diagnoses.</p>",
"</dd>",
"<dt><a href='#Section1'>Food poisoning</a></dt>",
"<dd id='Section1'>",
"<p><strong>Sign & Symptoms:</strong> Travel history or ingestion of high-risk foods may suggest food poisoning.The acute phase of food poisoning is less likely to be associated closely with motion provocation and may persist after motion.A combination of nausea and diarrhoea with severe stomach cramps is more likely with food poisoning.",
"<br><strong>Test:</strong> May identify aetiological agents from faecal samples.</p>",
"</dd>",
"<dt><a href='#Section2'>Acute vestibular disorder</a></dt>",
"<dd id='Section2'>",
"<p><strong>Sign & Symptoms:</strong> Dizziness (in the form of rotatory vertigo) with nystagmus and gait ataxia will be dominant features that accompany nausea and vomiting.",
"<br><strong>Test:</strong> Investigations such as audiology or MRI of the head may exclude specific pathologies.</p>",
"</dd>",
"</dl>"].join("\n");